<lb n="1114b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1114b06" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 392</head>
<lb n="1114b07" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛滅度後棺<note n="1114007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斂＝歛【宮】</note><app n="1114007"><lem wit="【大】">斂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">歛</rdg></app>葬送經
<note n="1114008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一名…經〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一名…經〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114008" word-count="6"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一名比丘師經</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1114b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1114b09" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="1114009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1114009"><lem wit="【大】">人名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>今附西晉錄</byline>
<lb n="1114b10" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT12p1114b1001">聞如是：</p><p id="pT12p1114b1004" place="inline">一時眾祐遊於華氏國。阿難以人定
<lb n="1114b11" ed="T"/>時，白眾祐言：「眾祐滅訖之後，棺<note n="1114010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斂＝殮【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1114010"><lem wit="【大】">斂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">殮</rdg></app>尊身，其
<lb n="1114b12" ed="T"/>禮云何？」</p><p id="pT12p1114b1204" place="inline">眾祐曰：「且自憂身，無憂佛也。吾滅度
<lb n="1114b13" ed="T"/>後，當有梵志、理家盡禮葬送。」</p><p id="pT12p1114b1312" place="inline">阿難言：「其禮云
<lb n="1114b14" ed="T"/>何？」</p><p id="pT12p1114b1402" place="inline">眾祐曰：「如飛行皇帝送喪之儀。」</p><p id="pT12p1114b1414" place="inline">重曰：「願聞
<lb n="1114b15" ed="T"/>儀則。」</p><p id="pT12p1114b1503" place="inline">眾祐曰：「聖帝崩時，以劫波育&CB00626;千張纏
<lb n="1114b16" ed="T"/>身，香澤灌上令澤下徹；以香<note n="1114011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00036;＝藉【宮】</note><app n="1114011"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00036;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">藉</rdg></app>身，上下四面
<lb n="1114b17" ed="T"/>使其齊同；放火闍維，撿骨、香汁洗，盛以金甕。
<lb n="1114b18" ed="T"/>石為&CB01073;&CB01033;——縱廣三尺，厚一尺——四邊上下各安
<lb n="1114b19" ed="T"/>一枚，金甕置中。跱剎懸繒具供所應，起土為
<lb n="1114b20" ed="T"/>塔，華香供養。</p><p id="pT12p1114b2006" place="inline">「佛當踰<note n="1114012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔彼〕－【宮】</note><app n="1114012"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。所以然者，吾自無
<lb n="1114b21" ed="T"/>數劫，以四等弘慈，行六度無極，經緯十方拯
<lb n="1114b22" ed="T"/>濟群生，功<note n="1114013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">德＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德＝福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114013"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>隆赫，成斯如來、無所著、正真道、
<lb n="1114b23" ed="T"/>最正覺、道法御、天人師，至尊難齊。各以把土
<lb n="1114b24" ed="T"/>供養塔者，其福無量。</p><p id="pT12p1114b2409" place="inline">「末世穢濁，民有顛沛之
<lb n="1114b25" ed="T"/>命，財有五家之分。吾以是故，留舍利并&CB00425;以
<lb n="1114b26" ed="T"/><note n="1114014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穰＝禳【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">穰＝禳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114014"><lem wit="【大】">穰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禳</rdg></app>世顛沛之禍，安祐眾生。為宗廟像令民&CB00418;，
<lb n="1114b27" ed="T"/>則沙門以經<note n="1114015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">導＝道【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">導＝道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114015"><lem wit="【大】">導</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">道</rdg></app>化未聞，令生者永去牢獄之
<lb n="1114b28" ed="T"/>酷、死者免三塗之罪，必獲昇天。若為佛廟，當
<lb n="1114b29" ed="T"/>令<note n="1114016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">踰＝殊【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">踰＝殊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114016"><lem wit="【大】">踰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">殊</rdg></app>彼矣。」</p><p id="pT12p1114b2905" place="inline">阿難言：「&CB00425;當如之？」</p><p id="pT12p1114b2912" place="inline">佛言：「吾&CB00425;者，
<pb n="1114c" id="T12.0392.1114c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1114c01" ed="T"/>四天大王之所獻也，合四以為一。佛所食器，
<lb n="1114c02" ed="T"/>群生慎無以食矣。</p><p id="pT12p1114c0208" place="inline">「滅度之後，諸國諍之、民心
<lb n="1114c03" ed="T"/>邪荒、賤命貴婬、背孝尊妖，&CB00425;當變化現五色
<lb n="1114c04" ed="T"/>光，飛行昇降，開化民心。黎庶&CB00418;之，追存佛
<lb n="1114c05" ed="T"/>德，去愚即明，順<note n="1114017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">用＝明【明】</note><app n="1114017"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">明</rdg></app>正教，皆興<note n="1114018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">廟＝佛【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">廟＝佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114018"><lem wit="【大】">廟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛</rdg></app>寺，旌表佛
<lb n="1114c06" ed="T"/>德。</p><p id="pT12p1114c0602" place="inline">「轉當東遊，所歷諸國凶疫消歇、君<note n="1114019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣＝民【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣＝民【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114019"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">民</rdg></app>康
<lb n="1114c07" ed="T"/>休、穀帛豐<note n="1114020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穰＝壤【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1114020"><lem wit="【大】">穰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">壤</rdg></app>、欣懌無患，終遠三塗，皆獲生
<lb n="1114c08" ed="T"/>天。極東國王仁而有明，&CB00425;當翔彼。王崩之
<lb n="1114c09" ed="T"/>後，其嗣婬荒，廢真從邪。民心亦爾，&CB00418;&CB00425;無
<lb n="1114c10" ed="T"/>肅敬之禮。天、龍見之，悲喜迎&CB00425;還海供奉。</p><p id="pT12p1114c1017" place="inline">「王
<lb n="1114c11" ed="T"/>亡尊&CB00425;，憂忿交胸，布告諸國：『購&CB00425;千金。』連年
<lb n="1114c12" ed="T"/>募之，令出首尾。民貪重賞，遍索不得。時有賤
<lb n="1114c13" ed="T"/>人，其名曰師，<note n="1114021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偽＝訛【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1114021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">偽＝訛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1114021"><lem wit="【大】">偽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">訛</rdg></app>作比丘，饕餮酒食，妻居育
<lb n="1114c14" ed="T"/>子。當醉提兒詣宮門言：『吾知&CB00425;處。』王聞大喜，
<lb n="1114c15" ed="T"/>請沙門入，曰：『&CB00425;所在乎？』<note n="1114022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">對＝答【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">對＝答【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114022"><lem wit="【大】">對</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">答</rdg></app>曰：『先以金來。』王
<lb n="1114c16" ed="T"/>賜金千斤。師曰：『<note n="1114023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114023"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>沙門當盜之耳。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c1614" place="inline">「即下書
<lb n="1114c17" ed="T"/><note n="1114024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">考＝拷【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">考＝拷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114024"><lem wit="【大】">考</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">拷</rdg></app>推諸沙門。其毒酷<note n="1114025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">烈＝裂【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1114025"><lem wit="【大】">烈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">裂</rdg></app>，臣民&CB00418;之靡不怨
<lb n="1114c18" ed="T"/>王。王曰：『爾為誰沙門乎？』答曰：『吾師事佛。』王
<lb n="1114c19" ed="T"/>曰：『佛有何戒<note n="1114026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔耶〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔耶〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114026"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>？』師曰：『有二百五十戒。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c1915" place="inline">「王曰：
<lb n="1114c20" ed="T"/>『<note n="1114027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">首＝守【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">首＝守【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114027"><lem wit="【大】">首</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">守</rdg></app>戒云何？』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2005" place="inline">「答曰：『第一當遵慈。仁普惠<note n="1114028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恩＋（施逮）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恩＋（施逮）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114028"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">恩施逮</rdg></app>及
<lb n="1114c21" ed="T"/>群生，視天下群生身命若己身命；慈濟悲愍，
<lb n="1114c22" ed="T"/>恕己安彼，道喜開化，護彼若身。潤逮草木，無
<lb n="1114c23" ed="T"/>虛<note n="1114029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01029;＝機【明】</note><app n="1114029"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01029;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">機</rdg></app>絕也。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2305" place="inline">「王曰：『善哉！佛之仁化懷天裹地，
<lb n="1114c24" ed="T"/>何生不賴焉？』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2406" place="inline">「『二當遵清。無積穢寶，尊榮國土，
<lb n="1114c25" ed="T"/>非有無篡；草芥之屬，非惠不取。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2513" place="inline">「王曰：『善哉！斯
<lb n="1114c26" ed="T"/>可謂清白者也。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2607" place="inline">「『三當遵貞。心無存婬、口無言
<lb n="1114c27" ed="T"/>調，偽聲邪色，一不視聽。&CB00418;彼<note n="1114030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婦＝羸【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婦＝羸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114030"><lem wit="【大】">婦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">羸</rdg></app>人，以母、以
<lb n="1114c28" ed="T"/>姊、以妹、以女，寧就燔身無為婬亂。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2814" place="inline">「王曰：『善哉！
<lb n="1114c29" ed="T"/>摸真景淨，佛<note n="1114031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化為＝為化【三】【宮】</note><note n="1114031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化為＝為化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1114031"><lem wit="【大】">化為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為化</rdg></app>首矣。』</p><p id="pT12p1114c2910" place="inline">「『四當慎言。無兩舌、惡
<pb n="1115a" id="T12.0392.1115a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1115a01" ed="T"/>罵、妄言、綺語、前譽後<note n="1115001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毀＝謗【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毀＝謗【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115001"><lem wit="【大】">毀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">謗</rdg></app>、證入無辜、蠱道鬼
<lb n="1115a02" ed="T"/>妖、厭禱<note n="1115002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;咀＝祝詛【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00057;咀＝祝詛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115002"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00057;咀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祝詛</rdg></app>。寧就吞炭，不出毒聲也。』</p><p id="pT12p1115a0215" place="inline">「王曰：
<lb n="1115a03" ed="T"/>『善哉佛化。惴惴<note n="1115003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慓慓＝慄慄【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慓慓＝慄慄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115003"><lem wit="【大】">慓慓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">慄慄</rdg></app>，慎言乃如茲乎。』</p><p id="pT12p1115a0315" place="inline">「『五當
<lb n="1115a04" ed="T"/>絕酒。<note n="1115004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝若【明】</note><app n="1115004"><lem wit="【大】">夫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">若</rdg></app>酒者，令君不仁、臣不忠、親不義、子
<lb n="1115a05" ed="T"/>不孝、婦人奢婬，<note n="1115005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">厥＝蹶【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1115005"><lem wit="【大】">厥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">蹶</rdg></app>失三十有六，亡國破家
<lb n="1115a06" ed="T"/>靡不由茲。寧飲毒而死，不<note n="1115006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酒亂＝醉【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酒亂＝醉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115006"><lem wit="【大】">酒亂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">醉</rdg></app>而生矣。』</p><p id="pT12p1115a0616" place="inline">「王
<lb n="1115a07" ed="T"/>曰：『善哉！佛之明化令吞德懷道，滅于眾惡、興
<lb n="1115a08" ed="T"/>于諸善；清淨為身、<note n="1115007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淡泊＝憺怕【宮】</note><app n="1115007"><lem wit="【大】">淡泊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">憺怕</rdg></app>為志。經化令仁，而
<lb n="1115a09" ed="T"/>爾教吾令殺；戒云守清<note n="1115008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔淨無貪〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔淨無貪〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115008"><lem wit="【大】">淨、無貪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>，而爾偷金；
<lb n="1115a10" ed="T"/>戒云無婬，而爾畜妻；戒當盡誠，而爾虛譖沙
<lb n="1115a11" ed="T"/>門，云其盜&CB00425;，令吾罪無辜；戒無嗜酒，而爾醉
<lb n="1115a12" ed="T"/>來。外諸沙門有具斯五德為高行者不乎？』</p><p id="pT12p1115a1217" place="inline">「答
<lb n="1115a13" ed="T"/>曰：『其為凶穢，甚於吾矣。』</p><p id="pT12p1115a1310" place="inline">「王問有司：『諸沙門何
<lb n="1115a14" ed="T"/>以為業？』</p><p id="pT12p1115a1404" place="inline">「對曰：『分衛無度，其為眾穢，甚於彼師
<lb n="1115a15" ed="T"/>矣。』</p><p id="pT12p1115a1502" place="inline">「王曰：『佛戒有二百五十——仁過、<note n="1115009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁＝二【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仁＝二【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115009"><lem wit="【大】">仁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">二</rdg></app>儀、清等、
<lb n="1115a16" ed="T"/>太素、貞齊、虛空——信若四時，明跨日月。緣得斯
<lb n="1115a17" ed="T"/>類篡法服、偷應器、<app type="＊" source="1114021"><lem wit="【大】">偽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">訛</rdg></app>為沙門，亂正真乎？一
<lb n="1115a18" ed="T"/>戒不奉，而云二百五十。』&CB00330;有司曰：『佛清淨廟，
<lb n="1115a19" ed="T"/>賢聖所宗；非鳥獸之巢窟。逐出穢濁者，無令
<lb n="1115a20" ed="T"/>止佛廟矣。』</p><p id="pT12p1115a2005" place="inline">「國之君子欲興<note n="1115010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝剎【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＝剎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115010"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">剎</rdg></app>廟，惟無快賢
<lb n="1115a21" ed="T"/>處中宣佛神化者，<note n="1115011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抆＝收【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">抆＝收【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115011"><lem wit="【大】">抆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">收</rdg></app>淚而止。自<note n="1115012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝思【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斯＝思【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115012"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">思</rdg></app>大道陵
<lb n="1115a22" ed="T"/>遲，神化日衰。」</p><p id="pT12p1115a2206" place="inline">佛告阿難：「吾<note n="1115013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔雖〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔雖〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115013"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>滅度後留&CB00425;
<lb n="1115a23" ed="T"/>及舍利，若有賢者肅心奉養，終皆昇天。」</p><p id="pT12p1115a2316" place="inline">阿難
<lb n="1115a24" ed="T"/>言：「千歲之末，&CB00425;現神德變化若茲，豈況無上
<lb n="1115a25" ed="T"/>正真道最正覺之靈化乎？」</p><p id="pT12p1115a2511" place="inline">佛說經時，天、龍、鬼
<lb n="1115a26" ed="T"/>神、王臣四輩，靡不哽咽，稽首而去。</p>
<lb n="1115a27" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛滅度後棺<anchor id="fxT12p1115a02"/>斂葬送經</jhead></juan></div1>
